                <article>
                    <h3>A new day a new owed app!</h3>
                    <p>Say hello to a completely reimagined way to track and settle debts! The new Owed+ app features a fresh, modern interface designed from the ground up to make managing your IOUs effortless and enjoyable.</p>

                    <p>What's New:
                    Cross-Platform Freedom – Access your account seamlessly across all your devices. Start on your iPhone, check in on your iPad, and manage everything from your Mac desktop.</p>

                    <p>Enhanced Visibility – Choose from our new color palettes designed with improved contrast in mind, ensuring everyone can use Owed+ comfortably and clearly.</p>

                    <p>Request Money in Seconds – Send payment requests directly via text message for Apple Pay, PayPal, and Venmo. No more awkward conversations or forgotten debts – tap, text, and get paid.</p>

                    <p>Make It Yours – Personalize your experience by selecting from multiple app icon designs that match your style.</p>

                    <p>Meet Gus, Your Helpful Guide – Say hello to Gus, our friendly pig mascot! Gus is here to walk you through the new app, share helpful tips, and make getting started a breeze. Whether you're new to Owed+ or returning to explore all the improvements, Gus has got your back.</p>

                    <p><span>The new Owed+ app isn't just an update – it's a complete transformation designed to make tracking who owes what simpler, faster, and more accessible than ever before.</span></p>
